He passed on all his traits to me and then acts shocked when we “disagree” 🙄

Jokes apart, I’m so grateful to him - unlike every other daughter, I won’t thank you for spoiling me (you’ve done a lot of that) but I will for making me resilient and independent by telling me “if you’re capable of starting a business, I’m sure you can figure this out by yourself” when I come to you with questions about taxes, insurance, investments or paperwork. 
Divyansh might look like you, but well we both know, I think like you and I’m blessed that I do! 

Happy Father’s Day Dad, I love you ❤️

latestPosts.caption:
The new @labelprernamehra collection is a true embodiment of how much I, our brand, and my personal style have grown - while still holding true to what we’ve always been known for

It has the most stunning modern draped sarees for the new gen IT girl, embellished to make her stand out but versatile so they’re timeless investments. Corsets and draped skirts that show beautiful the female form can be, and embroidery detailing that makes me say “I’ve outdone myself” 

I already have you guys a sneak peak on my stories when Alia wore her Gucci saree so you knew we did it first 🤭

But i genuinely cannot wait to show you all the pieces in their whole glory - videos, images, styling - the whole Schbang! 

You guys asked for more pearl pieces, well we delivered! (Swipe till the last frame) 

Launching on 13.06.2025

Still confused about what to name it, help me decide? 

Evara - Light, ethereal, and modern

Saaz - “Melody” - beauty in structure and styling

Ziya - “Radiance” - modern yet traditional, with a shimmer of embellishment

Meher - A poetic nod to the designer’s name; means “grace” or “kindness”

📷 @thetiltedlens
